*.crt
*.cert
*secret*
*password*
# Token secrets by ARTIFACT shape, not blanket *token* — the blanket silently
# dropped a legitimate test file (test_intent_dispatch_token_gate.py,
# 2026-07-07) and had already needed a tokens.py exception. Source/tests/docs
# with "token" in the name are trackable; credential-shaped files are not.
*.token
*.tokens
*token*.json
*token*.yaml
*token*.yml
*token*.toml
*token*.txt
*token*.env
*token*.secret
*api_key*
